OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FThe King and Queen have landed in the
OL,7,FUnited States to begin their state
OL,8,Fvisit to the country amid delicate
OL,9,Frelations between the UK and the US.
OL,11,FThey are now on their way to the White
OL,12,FHouse, where President Donald Trump
OL,13,Fand First Lady Melania Trump will meet
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FThey will then go for tea in the Green
OL,17,FRoom of the White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FThe trip coincides with the 250th
OL,7,Fanniversary of the signing of the
OL,8,FDeclaration of Independence, with much
OL,9,Fof King Charles's visit centred around
OL,10,Fthe celebrations.
OL,12,FBut the King is playing a delicate
OL,13,Frole with President Donald Trump, who,
OL,14,Fwhile being a known fan of the British
OL,15,FRoyal Family, has fallen out with Keir
OL,16,FStarmer in recent months, particularly
OL,17,Fover the UK's reluctance to get
OL,18,Finvolved in the Iran war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FTrump has criticised Starmer,
OL,7,Fdismissing him as not "Winston
OL,8,FChurchill" and urging him to change
OL,9,Fcourse on numerous policy areas.
OL,11,FRecent leaks have also suggested the
OL,12,FUS could even go as far as reassessing
OL,13,FWashington's support for the
OL,14,Fsovereignty over the Falkland Islands,
OL,15,Fa realm where the King is sovereign.
OL,17,FA shooting at a Washington dinner
OL,18,Fattended by President Donald Trump on
OL,19,FSaturday sparked a last-minute
OL,20,Fsecurity review of the four-day state
OL,21,Fvisit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FThe president has insisted the
OL,7,Fpolitical chill won't affect the royal
OL,8,Fvisit, saying Charles "has nothing to
OL,9,Fdo with that," and making positive
OL,10,Fstatements about the potential the
OL,11,FKing has to repair relations.
OL,13,FThe president has spoken in glowing
OL,14,Fterms about Charles, repeatedly
OL,15,Freferring to the monarch as his
OL,16,F"friend" and a "great guy."
OL,26,@pD@WOUxD@AOUxD@HO]xD@POUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FThe King must also contend with the
OL,7,Fshadow of his younger brother, Andrew
OL,8,FMountbatten-Windsor, who has faced
OL,9,Fnumerous calls by US lawmakers to
OL,10,Fappear in front of Congress to discuss
OL,11,Fhis relationship with disgraced
OL,12,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,14,FAndrew has denied ever committing
OL,15,Fcrimes, but Epstein victims have urged
OL,16,Fthe king to meet with them and other
OL,17,Fsexual abuse survivors
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
