OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FCharles has visited the US 19 times,
OL,7,Fbut this is his first state visit to
OL,8,Fthe country since becoming king in
OL,9,F2022. His mother, Queen Elizabeth II,
OL,10,Fmade four state visits to the US.
OL,12,FThe preparations have been underway
OL,13,Ffor weeks, with the British embassy in
OL,14,Fthe US sharing a little bit of the
OL,15,Finformation behind what has gone into
OL,16,Fthe visit.
OL,18,FOn Monday, they shared a post on X,
OL,19,Fwhich showed chefs making food for 650
OL,20,Fpeople, with around 3,000 sandwiches
OL,21,Fbeing made for an afternoon tea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FSandwich offerings include Scottish
OL,7,Fsmoked salmon, egg mayonnaise, British
OL,8,Froast beef and pickled cucumber, with
OL,9,Fscones and clotted cream for dessert.
OL,11,FWhat's on the agenda for the state
OL,12,Fvisit?
OL,14,FAfter tea, Charles and Camilla will
OL,15,Fjoin the President and First Lady for
OL,16,Fa tour of the newly expanded White
OL,17,FHouse Beehive, which is nestled on the
OL,18,FSouth Lawn near the White House
OL,19,FKitchen Garden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
