OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Trump and Melania will
OL,7,Fhost a State Arrival Ceremony on the
OL,8,FSouth Lawn of the White House.
OL,10,FDrawing upon a tradition that dates
OL,11,Fback to the 18th century, the couple
OL,12,Fwill mark the official arrival of the
OL,13,Froyals with a traditional military
OL,14,Farrival ceremony, which includes
OL,15,Fmilitary honours by the US Army Herald
OL,16,FTrumpets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FNational anthems of both countries
OL,7,Fwill be played by "The President's
OL,8,FOwn" US Marine Band, with the
OL,9,FPresidential Salute Battery rendering
OL,10,Fa 21-gun cannon salute.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe president and the king will also
OL,18,Fhave a one-on-one meeting on Tuesday.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
