CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FA key moment will be the king's speech
OL,7,Fto the US Congress on Tuesday. It's
OL,8,Fonly the second time, after Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth II in 1991, that a UK
OL,10,Fmonarch has addressed a joint meeting
OL,11,Fof both houses.
OL,13,FTuesday evening will be the
OL,14,Fculmination of the trip with Trump and
OL,15,FMelania greeting the royals upon their
OL,16,Farrival at the South Portico of the
OL,17,FWhite House for a State Dinner in the
OL,18,FEast Room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FThe royal couple will also visit the
OL,7,FSeptember 11 memorial in New York on
OL,8,FWednesday and attend a 250th birthday
OL,9,Fblock party in Virginia, where Charles
OL,10,Fwill also meet Indigenous leaders
OL,11,Finvolved in nature conservation.
OL,13,FOn Thursday morning, Charles and
OL,14,FCamilla will return to the White House.
OL,16,FThe president and first lady will
OL,17,Fgreet them at the South Portico and
OL,18,Fsay their farewells in the Diplomatic
OL,19,FReception Room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
