PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777363547
OL,3,CKing and Queen land in US for four-day
OL,4,Cstate visit
OL,6,FAt the end of the trip, Charles will
OL,7,Ftravel solo to Bermuda for a three-day
OL,8,Froyal visit - his first to a British
OL,9,FOverseas Territory as King.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
